article.headline: Christmas scores 17, Longwood knocks off Delaware State 84-82 in double overtime

images.name: Johnathan Massie makes beautiful dish for a basket
images.caption: Johnathan Massie makes beautiful dish for a basket

article.linkText: Christmas scores 17, Longwood knocks off Delaware State 84-82 in double overtime
article.story: FARMVILLE, Va. -- — Michael Christmas had 17 points in Longwood's 84-82 double-overtime win against Delaware State on Friday night. Christmas was 3 of 9 shooting and 11 of 11 from the free throw line for the Lancers (4-1). D'Avian Houston shot 5 for 7, including 4 for 6 from beyond the arc to add 16 points. Johnathan Massie shot 2 for 16 (2 for 9 from 3-point range) and 8 of 13 from the free throw line to finish with 14 points, while adding nine rebounds. Martez Robinson led the Hornets (1-5) in scoring, finishing with 24 points, nine rebounds and five steals. Jevin Muniz added 22 points and six rebounds for Delaware State. Deywilk Tavarez also had 19 points, five assists and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
